trans-unit.source: Specifies the type of elements in the queue.
trans-unit.target: 指定佇列中項目的類型。

trans-unit.source: Represents a first-in, first-out collection of objects.
trans-unit.target: 表示物件的先進先出 (FIFO) 集合。

trans-unit.source: This class implements a generic queue as a circular array.
trans-unit.target: 這個類別會實作泛型佇列以循環的陣列。

trans-unit.source: Objects stored in a <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601> are inserted at one end and removed from the other.
trans-unit.target: 物件儲存在<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601>其中一端插入和移除不同的方式。

trans-unit.source: Queues and stacks are useful when you need temporary storage for information; that is, when you might want to discard an element after retrieving its value.
trans-unit.target: 佇列和堆疊有用您需要進行暫存儲存位置的資訊。也就是說，您可能想要擷取其值後捨棄項目。

trans-unit.source: Use <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601> if you need to access the information in the same order that it is stored in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 使用<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601>如果您需要存取相同的順序儲存在集合中的資訊。

trans-unit.source: Use <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601> if you need to access the information in reverse order.
trans-unit.target: 使用<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Stack%601>如果您需要以相反順序存取的資訊。

trans-unit.source: Use <xref:System.Collections.Concurrent.ConcurrentQueue%601> or <xref:System.Collections.Concurrent.ConcurrentStack%601> if you need to access the collection from multiple threads concurrently.
trans-unit.target: 使用<xref:System.Collections.Concurrent.ConcurrentQueue%601>或<xref:System.Collections.Concurrent.ConcurrentStack%601>如果您需要從多個執行緒同時存取集合。

trans-unit.source: Three main operations can be performed on a <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601> and its elements:
trans-unit.target: 可以對三個主要作業<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601>和其項目：

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enqueue%2A> adds an element to the end of the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enqueue%2A> 將元素加入結尾<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601>。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Dequeue%2A> removes the oldest element from the start of the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Dequeue%2A> 從開始移除最舊的項目<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601>。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Peek%2A> peek returns the oldest element that is at the start of the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601> but does not remove it from the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Peek%2A> 查看傳回的最舊的項目開頭，<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601>但不會移除從<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601>。

trans-unit.source: The capacity of a <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601> is the number of elements the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601> can hold.
trans-unit.target: 容量<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601>是項目數目<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601>可以保存。

trans-unit.source: As elements are added to a <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601>, the capacity is automatically increased as required by reallocating the internal array.
trans-unit.target: 當項目加入至<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601>，就會自動增加容量的要求以重新配置內部的陣列。

trans-unit.source: The capacity can be decreased by calling <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.TrimExcess%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 藉由呼叫，您可以減少容量<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.TrimExcess%2A>。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601> accepts `null` as a valid value for reference types and allows duplicate elements.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601> 接受`null`參考有效的值類型，並允許重複的項目。

trans-unit.target: 下列程式碼範例示範幾個方法來<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601>泛型類別。

trans-unit.source: The code example creates a queue of strings with default capacity and uses the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enqueue%2A> method to queue five strings.
trans-unit.target: 程式碼範例會建立字串的佇列預設容量，並使用<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enqueue%2A>佇列五個字串的方法。

trans-unit.source: The elements of the queue are enumerated, which does not change the state of the queue.
trans-unit.target: 列舉佇列的項目，這不會變更佇列的狀態。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Dequeue%2A> method is used to dequeue the first string.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Dequeue%2A>方法用來清除佇列的第一個字串。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Peek%2A> method is used to look at the next item in the queue, and then the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Dequeue%2A> method is used to dequeue it.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Peek%2A>方法用來查看佇列中下一個項目，然後<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Dequeue%2A>方法用來從佇列中清除。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.ToArray%2A> method is used to create an array and copy the queue elements to it, then the array is passed to the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.%23ctor%2A> constructor that takes <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable%601>, creating a copy of the queue.

trans-unit.source: The elements of the copy are displayed.
trans-unit.target: 複製的項目會顯示。

trans-unit.source: An array twice the size of the queue is created, and the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.CopyTo%2A> method is used to copy the array elements beginning at the middle of the array.
trans-unit.target: 兩次的佇列大小建立陣列，而<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.CopyTo%2A>方法用來複製開始中間之陣列的陣列元素。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.%23ctor%2A> constructor is used again to create a second copy of the queue containing three null elements at the beginning.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.%23ctor%2A>建構函式一次用來建立包含三個開頭的 null 項目佇列的第二個副本。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Contains%2A> method is used to show that the string "four" is in the first copy of the queue, after which the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Clear%2A> method clears the copy and the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Count%2A> property shows that the queue is empty.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Contains%2A>方法用來顯示"4"的字串是在佇列中的第一個複本之後<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Clear%2A>方法清除複製和<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Count%2A>屬性會顯示佇列是空的。

trans-unit.source: Public static (<see langword="Shared" /> in Visual Basic) members of this type are thread safe.
trans-unit.target: 公用靜態 (<see langword="Shared" />在 Visual Basic 中) 這種類型的成員都具備執行緒安全。

trans-unit.source: Any instance members are not guaranteed to be thread safe.
trans-unit.target: 不保證任何執行個體成員是安全執行緒。

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.Queue`1" /> can support multiple readers concurrently, as long as the collection is not modified.
trans-unit.target: A<see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.Queue`1" />可以支援多個讀取器同時，只要未修改集合。

trans-unit.source: Even so, enumerating through a collection is intrinsically not a thread-safe procedure.
trans-unit.target: 即便如此，列舉集合在本質上並非安全執行緒程序。

trans-unit.source: To guarantee thread safety during enumeration, you can lock the collection during the entire enumeration.
trans-unit.target: 若要確保列舉期間的執行緒安全性，您可以在整個列舉期間鎖定集合。

trans-unit.source: To allow the collection to be accessed by multiple threads for reading and writing, you must implement your own synchronization.
trans-unit.target: 若要讓多重執行緒能夠存取集合以便進行讀取和寫入，您必須實作自己的同步處理。

trans-unit.source: The `foreach` statement of the C# language (`for each` in C++, `For Each` in Visual Basic) hides the complexity of the enumerators.
trans-unit.target: `foreach` C# 語言的陳述式 (`for each` c + +`For Each`在 Visual Basic 中) 會隱藏列舉值的複雜度。

trans-unit.source: Therefore, using `foreach` is recommended, instead of directly manipulating the enumerator.
trans-unit.target: 因此，建議您使用 `foreach`，而不要直接使用列舉值。

trans-unit.source: Enumerators can be used to read the data in the collection, but they cannot be used to modify the underlying collection.
trans-unit.target: 列舉程式可以用來讀取集合中的資料，但是無法用來修改基礎集合。

trans-unit.source: Initially, the enumerator is positioned before the first element in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 一開始，列舉程式位在集合中的第一個項目之前。

trans-unit.source: At this position, <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.Current%2A> is undefined.
trans-unit.target: 在這個位置上，<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.Current%2A> 並未定義。

trans-unit.source: Therefore, you must call <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> to advance the enumerator to the first element of the collection before reading the value of <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.Current%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 因此，在讀取 <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> 的值之前，必須呼叫 <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.Current%2A> 以將列舉值前移至集合的第一個項目。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.Current%2A> returns the same object until <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> is called.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.Current%2A> 會傳回相同的物件直到呼叫 <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A>。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> sets <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.Current%2A> to the next element.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> 會將 <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.Current%2A> 設定為下一個項目。

trans-unit.source: If <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> passes the end of the collection, the enumerator is positioned after the last element in the collection and <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> returns `false`.
trans-unit.target: 如果<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A>超過集合的列舉值的結尾會位於集合中的最後一個元素之後和<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A>傳回`false`。

trans-unit.source: When the enumerator is at this position, subsequent calls to <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> also return `false`.
trans-unit.target: 列舉值位於這個位置上，後續呼叫<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A>也會傳回`false`。

trans-unit.source: If the last call to <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> returned `false`, <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.Current%2A> is undefined.
trans-unit.target: 如果最後一個呼叫<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A>傳回`false`，<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.Current%2A>是未定義。

trans-unit.source: You cannot set <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.Current%2A> to the first element of the collection again; you must create a new enumerator instance instead.
trans-unit.target: 您不能再次將 <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.Current%2A> 設定為集合的第一個項目；您必須建立新的列舉值執行個體。

trans-unit.source: An enumerator remains valid as long as the collection remains unchanged.
trans-unit.target: 只要集合維持不變，列舉程式就持續有效。

trans-unit.source: If changes are made to the collection, such as adding, modifying, or deleting elements, the enumerator is irrecoverably invalidated and the next call to <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> or <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.System%23Collections%23IEnumerator%23Reset%2A> throws an <xref:System.InvalidOperationException>.
trans-unit.target: 如果變更集合，例如加入、 修改或刪除項目，列舉程式會永久失效，而且下次呼叫<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A>或<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.System%23Collections%23IEnumerator%23Reset%2A>會擲回<xref:System.InvalidOperationException>。

trans-unit.source: If the collection is modified between calling <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> method and obtaining the value of the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.Current%2A> property, <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.Current%2A> returns the element that it is set to, even if the enumerator is already invalidated.
trans-unit.target: 如果呼叫之間修改集合<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A>方法並取得的值<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.Current%2A>屬性，<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Enumerator.Current%2A>傳回項目所設定，即使列舉值已經無效。

trans-unit.source: The enumerator does not have exclusive access to the collection; therefore, enumerating through a collection is intrinsically not a thread-safe procedure.
trans-unit.target: 列舉程式沒有集合的獨佔存取權，因此，列舉集合內容本質上並不是安全的執行緒程序。

trans-unit.source: To guarantee thread safety during enumeration, you can lock the collection during the entire enumeration.
trans-unit.target: 若要確保列舉期間的執行緒安全性，您可以在整個列舉期間鎖定集合。

trans-unit.source: To allow the collection to be accessed by multiple threads for reading and writing, you must implement your own synchronization.
trans-unit.target: 若要讓多重執行緒能夠存取集合以便進行讀取和寫入，您必須實作自己的同步處理。

trans-unit.source: Default implementations of collections in <xref:System.Collections.Generic?displayProperty=nameWithType> are not synchronized.
trans-unit.target: 集合中的預設實作<xref:System.Collections.Generic?displayProperty=nameWithType>未同步處理。

trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.ToArray%2A>方法用來建立陣列，並將佇列項目複製到它，然後將陣列傳遞至<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.%23ctor%2A>建構函式<xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable%601>，建立佇列的複本。

trans-unit.source: The elements of the copy are displayed.
trans-unit.target: 複製的項目會顯示。

trans-unit.source: An array twice the size of the queue is created, and the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.CopyTo%2A> method is used to copy the array elements beginning at the middle of the array.
trans-unit.target: 兩次的佇列大小建立陣列，而<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.CopyTo%2A>方法用來複製開始中間之陣列的陣列元素。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.%23ctor%2A> constructor is used again to create a second copy of the queue containing three null elements at the beginning.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.%23ctor%2A>建構函式一次用來建立包含三個開頭的 null 項目佇列的第二個副本。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Contains%2A> method is used to show that the string "four" is in the first copy of the queue, after which the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Clear%2A> method clears the copy and the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Count%2A> property shows that the queue is empty.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Contains%2A>方法用來顯示"4"的字串是在佇列中的第一個複本之後<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Clear%2A>方法清除複製和<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Count%2A>屬性會顯示佇列是空的。

trans-unit.source: Sets the capacity to the actual number of elements in the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.Queue`1" />, if that number is less than 90 percent of current capacity.
trans-unit.target: 如果該數目小於目前容量的 90%，則將容量設為 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.Queue`1" /> 中項目的實際數目。

trans-unit.source: This method can be used to minimize a collection's memory overhead if no new elements will be added to the collection.
trans-unit.target: 這個方法可用記憶體降到最低集合的額外負荷如果沒有新的項目會加入至集合。

trans-unit.source: The cost of reallocating and copying a large <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601> can be considerable, however, so the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.TrimExcess%2A> method does nothing if the list is at more than 90 percent of capacity.
trans-unit.target: 重新配置及複製大型的成本<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601>相當大，但是，可能會因此<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.TrimExcess%2A>方法沒有作用，如果清單是在超過容量的 90%。

trans-unit.source: This avoids incurring a large reallocation cost for a relatively small gain.
trans-unit.target: 這可避免產生大型重新配置成本相對較小的改善。

trans-unit.source: This method is an O(`n`) operation, where `n` is <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Count%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 這個方法是 O (`n`) 作業，其中`n`是<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Count%2A>。

trans-unit.source: To reset a <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601> to its initial state, call the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Clear%2A> method before calling <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.TrimExcess%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: 若要重設<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601>設為初始狀態，請呼叫<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.Clear%2A>方法之前先呼叫<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601.TrimExcess%2A>方法。

trans-unit.source: Trimming an empty <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601> sets the capacity of the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601> to the default capacity.
trans-unit.target: 修剪空白<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601>設定的容量<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Queue%601>預設容量。
